      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LANSLEY WHISPER (5) doesn't win out of turn. Finished in the money last time though when second (22.87) at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Must come into calculations. BLACKPOOL VIPER (7) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.87) at this track behind Speedy Cruella in a Grade 6. Got back and turned spotting a start but found the line impressively. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Hard to beat again. SIX STORY SYD (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a third place finish (30.30) at Northam the start prior. Better than last start and can bounce back. MAN ABOUT TOWN (1) looks an each-way chance.",
